    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Cone of Cold</strong> (Level 5 Evocation)</p><p>A blast of cold air erupts from your hands. Each creature in a 60-foot cone must make a constitution saving throw. A creature takes 8d8 cold damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>A creature killed by this spell becomes a frozen statue until it thaws.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 5th.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (A small crystal or glass cone.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Self | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Sorcerer, Wizard</em></p>",
